***Made to Order item ---> Minimum 3 business days to fabricate before shipping.

Listing is for (1) Pick your own color from Drop Down menu

Perfect little box to house those special mementos. This unique box design makes a great accessories for chest of drawers, desks and tables.

• Solid wood construction
• Pill box is painted with the color Green Apple, sanded and 2nd coated.
• Top is mounted with my "Polka Dotted Bunny" illustration design Print.
• Inside Base is left Natural, Inside Top is painted. (All Paint is Non- Toxic)
• Sealed with a high gloss sealer (also Non- Toxic)
• Signed on the bottom

The perfect companion piece to house those special mementos.

• Also, makes a great Tooth-fairy box.
• My First Tooth container
• My First curl
ADULT uses, this is the Perfect container for:
• (Sleeping) Pills
• Vitamins

Measurements:
Small Wooden Pill Boxes
1-9/16" wide x 1" tall

Contact me if you need more than one?
